# Slab patch corners
vertex 1 xyz 0.0 0.0 0.0
vertex 2 xyz 1.0 0.0 0.0
vertex 3 xyz 1.0 1.0 0.0
vertex 4 xyz 0.0 1.0 0.0

curve 1 vertex 1 2
curve 2 vertex 2 3
curve 3 vertex 3 4
curve 4 vertex 4 1

patch 1 normal 0 0 1 boundary curve 1 2 3 4 size def

# Rebar curve with independent vertices, offset from boundary so T3D does
# not merge them with patch nodes.
vertex 10 xyz 0.05 0.5 0.0
vertex 11 xyz 0.95 0.5 0.0
curve 5 vertex 10 11 output yes
